Through some experimentation I have discovered that if I start sshuttle with `sshuttle -l 12303 --dns -Nvvvr me@remote_host.example.com` and then `sudo iptables -t nat -D sshuttle-12303 4` and add the following to my BIND configuration:

```
zone "remote.domain.example.com" IN {
	type forward;
	forwarders port 12300 { 127.0.0.1; };
};

```

I get the behaviour I am desiring.

